  "description": {
    "en": "The National Institute of Statistics (INS) is the official national statistical authority of Romania, responsible for the collection, processing, and dissemination of official statistics on the Romanian economy, population, and society. INS produces data compliant with Eurostat and EU standards, covering GDP, population census, consumer prices, employment, trade, and agricultural statistics.",
    "zh": "罗马尼亚国家统计局（INS）是罗马尼亚官方国家统计机构，负责收集、处理和发布有关罗马尼亚经济、人口和社会的官方统计数据。INS生产符合欧盟统计局（Eurostat）标准的数据，涵盖GDP、人口普查、消费价格、就业、贸易和农业统计。"
  },
